semibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors line-clamp-1\">奥西耶克特夫尔贾（德拉瓦河畔保存极其完好的18世纪巴洛克风格哈布斯堡星形要塞建筑群）</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 line-clamp-1\">Tvrđa (Osijek)</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>",
